title: NFL’s Best-Kept Secrets
itunes:title: NFL’s Best-Kept Secrets
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – break down the latest news from the NFL including the Pro Bowl moving to Orlando and Rob Ryan’s comments on his time in New Orleans. Then the heroes discuss some of the best-kept secrets in the NFL and share which players are poised to have a break-out 2016.
